ti, tattaṁ ayokhīlaṁ dutiye hatthe gamenti, tattaṁ ayokhīlaṁ pāde gamenti, tattaṁ ayokhīlaṁ dutiye pāde gamenti, tattaṁ ayokhīlaṁ majjheurasmiṁ gamenti; ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:6.6":{"pli":"so tattha dukkhā tibbā kaṭukā vedanā vedeti; ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:6.7":{"pli":"na ca tāva kālaṁ karoti yāva na taṁ pāpakammaṁ byantī hotī”ti. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:6.8":{"pli":"Attheva suttantoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:6.9":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:6.10":{"pli":"Tena hi atthi nirayesu nirayapālāti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.3:7.1":{"pli":"Natthi nirayesu nirayapālāti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv20.3:7.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:7.3":{"pli":"Nanu vuttaṁ bhagavatā—","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:7.4":{"pli":"“tamenaṁ, bhikkhave, nirayapālā saṁvesetvā kuṭhārīhi tacchanti …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:7.5":{"pli":"tamenaṁ, bhikkhave, nirayapālā uddhampādaṁ adhosiraṁ ṭhapetvā vāsīhi tacchanti …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:7.6":{"pli":"tamenaṁ, bhikkhave, nirayapālā rathe yojetvā ādittāya pathaviyā sampajjalitāya sajotibhūtāya sārentipi paccāsārentipi …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:7.7":{"pli":"tamenaṁ, bhikkhave, nirayapālā mahantaṁ aṅgārapabbataṁ ādittaṁ sampajjalitaṁ sajotibhūtaṁ āropentipi oropentipi …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:7.8":{"pli":"tamenaṁ, bhikkhave, nirayapālā uddhampādaṁ adhosiraṁ gahetvā tattāya lohakumbhiyā pakkhipanti ādittāya sampajjalitāya sajotibhūtāya. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:7.9":{"pli":"So tattha pheṇuddehakaṁ paccati, so tattha pheṇuddehakaṁ paccamāno sakimpi uddhaṁ gacchati, sakimpi adho gacchati, sakimpi tiriyaṁ gacchati. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:7.10":{"pli":"So tattha dukkhā tibbā kaṭukā vedanā vedayati, na ca tāva kālaṁ karoti yāva na taṁ pāpakammaṁ byantīhoti. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:7.11":{"pli":"Tamenaṁ, bhikkhave, nirayapālā mahāniraye pakkhipanti. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:7.12":{"pli":"So kho pana, bhikkhave, mahānirayo—","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.3:8.1":{"pli":"Catukkaṇṇo catudvāro, ","html":"<blockquote class='gatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv20.3:8.2":{"pli":"vibhatto bhāgaso mito; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv20.3:8.3":{"pli":"Ayopākārapariyanto, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv20.3:8.4":{"pli":"ayasā paṭikujjito. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"kv20.3:9.1":{"pli":"Tassa ayomayā bhūmi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv20.3:9.2":{"pli":"Jalitā tejasā yutā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv20.3:9.3":{"pli":"Samantā yojanasataṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv20.3:9.4":{"pli":"Pharitvā tiṭṭhati sabbadā”ti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"kv20.3:10.1":{"pli":"Attheva suttantoti? ","html":"<p>{}"},"kv20.3:10.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.3:10.3":{"pli":"Tena hi atthi nirayesu nirayapālāti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.3:10.4":{"pli":"Nirayapālakathā niṭṭhitā. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"kv20.4":{"kv20.4:0.1":{"pli":"Kathāvatthu ","html":"<article id='kv20.4'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"kv20.4:0.2":{"pli":"Mahāpaṇṇāsaka ","html":"<li>{}</li>"},"kv20.4:0.3":{"pli":"Vīsatimavagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"kv20.4:0.4":{"pli":"Tiracchānakathā ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"kv20.4:1.1":{"pli":"Atthi devesu tiracchānagatāti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv20.4:1.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:1.3":{"pli":"Atthi tiracchānagatesu devāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:1.4":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:1.5":{"pli":"atthi devesu tiracchānagatāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:1.6":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:1.7":{"pli":"Devaloko tiracchānayonīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:1.8":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:1.9":{"pli":"atthi devesu tiracchānagatāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:1.10":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:1.11":{"pli":"Atthi tattha kīṭā paṭaṅgā makasā makkhikā ahī vicchikā satapadī gaṇḍuppādāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:1.12":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.4:2.1":{"pli":"Natthi devesu tiracchānagatāti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='heterodox'>{}"},"kv20.4:2.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:2.3":{"pli":"Nanu atthi tattha erāvaṇo nāma hatthināgo sahassayuttaṁ dibbaṁ yānanti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:2.4":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:2.5":{"pli":"Hañci atthi tattha erāvaṇo nāma hatthināgo sahassayuttaṁ dibbaṁ yānaṁ, tena vata re vattabbe—","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:2.6":{"pli":"“atthi devesu tiracchānagatā”ti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.4:3.1":{"pli":"Atthi devesu tiracchānagatāti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv20.4:3.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:3.3":{"pli":"Atthi tattha hatthibandhā assabandhā yāvasikā kāraṇikā bhattakārakāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:3.4":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.4:3.5":{"pli":"Tena hi natthi devesu tiracchānagatāti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.4:3.6":{"pli":"Tiracchānakathā niṭṭhitā. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"kv20.5":{"kv20.5:0.1":{"pli":"Kathāvatthu ","html":"<article id='kv20.5'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"kv20.5:0.2":{"pli":"Mahāpaṇṇāsaka ","html":"<li>{}</li>"},"kv20.5:0.3":{"pli":"Vīsatimavagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"kv20.5:0.4":{"pli":"Maggakathā ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"kv20.5:1.1":{"pli":"Pañcaṅgiko maggoti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv20.5:1.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:1.3":{"pli":"Nanu aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo vutto bhagavatā, seyyathidaṁ—","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:1.4":{"pli":"sammādiṭṭhi …pe… sammāsamādhīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:1.5":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:1.6":{"pli":"Hañci aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo vutto bhagavatā, seyyathidaṁ—","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:1.7":{"pli":"sammādiṭṭhi …pe… sammāsamādhi, no ca vata re vattabbe—","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:1.8":{"pli":"“pañcaṅgiko maggo”ti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.5:2.1":{"pli":"Pañcaṅgiko maggoti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv20.5:2.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:2.3":{"pli":"Nanu vuttaṁ bhagavatā—","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.5:3.1":{"pli":"“Maggānaṁ aṭṭhaṅgiko seṭṭho, ","html":"<blockquote class='gatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv20.5:3.2":{"pli":"Saccānaṁ caturo padā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv20.5:3.3":{"pli":"Virāgo seṭṭho dhammānaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv20.5:3.4":{"pli":"Dvipadānañca cakkhumā”ti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"kv20.5:4.1":{"pli":"Attheva suttantoti? ","html":"<p>{}"},"kv20.5:4.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:4.3":{"pli":"Tena hi aṭṭhaṅgiko maggoti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.5:5.1":{"pli":"Sammāvācā maggaṅgaṁ, sā ca na maggoti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv20.5:5.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:5.3":{"pli":"Sammādiṭṭhi maggaṅgaṁ, sā ca na maggoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:5.4":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:5.5":{"pli":"sammāvācā maggaṅgaṁ, sā ca na maggoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:5.6":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:5.7":{"pli":"Sammāsaṅkappo …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:5.8":{"pli":"sammāvāyāmo …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:5.9":{"pli":"sammāsati …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:5.10":{"pli":"sammāsamādhi maggaṅgaṁ, so ca na maggoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:5.11":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.5:6.1":{"pli":"Sammākammanto …pe… ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv20.5:6.2":{"pli":"sammāājīvo maggaṅgaṁ, so ca na maggoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:6.3":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:6.4":{"pli":"sammādiṭṭhi …pe… sammāsamādhi maggaṅgaṁ, so ca na maggoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:6.5":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.5:7.1":{"pli":"Sammādiṭṭhi maggaṅgaṁ, sā ca maggoti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv20.5:7.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:7.3":{"pli":"Sammāvācā maggaṅgaṁ, sā ca maggoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:7.4":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:7.5":{"pli":"sammādiṭṭhi maggaṅgaṁ, sā ca maggoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:7.6":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:7.7":{"pli":"Sammākammanto …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:7.8":{"pli":"sammāājīvo maggaṅgaṁ, so ca maggoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:7.9":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.5:8.1":{"pli":"Sammāsaṅkappo …pe… ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv20.5:8.2":{"pli":"sammāvāyāmo …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:8.3":{"pli":"sammāsati …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:8.4":{"pli":"sammāsamādhi maggaṅgaṁ, so ca maggoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:8.5":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:8.6":{"pli":"Sammāvācā …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:8.7":{"pli":"sammākammanto …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:8.8":{"pli":"sammāājīvo maggaṅgaṁ, so ca maggoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:8.9":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.5:9.1":{"pli":"Ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggoti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='heterodox'>{}"},"kv20.5:9.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:9.3":{"pli":"Nanu vuttaṁ bhagavatā—","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:9.4":{"pli":"“pubbeva kho panassa kāyakammaṁ vacīkammaṁ ājīvo suparisuddho hoti; ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:9.5":{"pli":"evamassāyaṁ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvanāpāripūriṁ gacchatī”ti. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:9.6":{"pli":"Attheva suttantoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:9.7":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:9.8":{"pli":"Tena hi pañcaṅgiko maggoti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.5:10.1":{"pli":"Pañcaṅgiko maggoti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv20.5:10.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:10.3":{"pli":"Nanu vuttaṁ bhagavatā—","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:10.4":{"pli":"“yasmiṁ kho, subhadda, dhammavinaye ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo na upalabbhati, samaṇopi tattha na upalabbhati, dutiyopi tattha samaṇo na upalabbhati, tatiyopi tattha samaṇo na upalabbhati, catutthopi tattha samaṇo na upalabbhati. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:10.5":{"pli":"Yasmiñca kho, subhadda, dhammavinaye ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo upalabbhati, samaṇopi tattha upalabbhati, dutiyopi …pe… tatiyopi …pe… catutthopi tattha samaṇo upalabbhati. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:10.6":{"pli":"Imasmiṁ kho, subhadda, dhammavinaye ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo upalabbhati. Idheva, subhadda, samaṇo, idha dutiyo samaṇo, idha tatiyo samaṇo, idha catuttho samaṇo. Suññā parappavādā samaṇebhi aññehī”ti. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:10.7":{"pli":"Attheva suttantoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:10.8":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.5:10.9":{"pli":"Tena hi aṭṭhaṅgiko maggoti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.5:10.10":{"pli":"Maggakathā niṭṭhitā. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"kv20.6":{"kv20.6:0.1":{"pli":"Kathāvatthu ","html":"<article id='kv20.6'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"kv20.6:0.2":{"pli":"Mahāpaṇṇāsaka ","html":"<li>{}</li>"},"kv20.6:0.3":{"pli":"Vīsatimavagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"kv20.6:0.4":{"pli":"Ñāṇakathā ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"kv20.6:1.1":{"pli":"Dvādasavatthukaṁ ñāṇaṁ lokuttaranti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv20.6:1.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.3":{"pli":"Dvādasa lokuttarañāṇānīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.4":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.5":{"pli":"dvādasa lokuttarañāṇānīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.6":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.7":{"pli":"Dvādasa sotāpattimaggāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.8":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.9":{"pli":"dvādasa sotāpattimaggāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.10":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.11":{"pli":"Dvādasa sotāpattiphalānīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.12":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.13":{"pli":"dvādasa sakadāgāmimaggā …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.14":{"pli":"anāgāmimaggā …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.15":{"pli":"arahattamaggāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.16":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.17":{"pli":"dvādasa arahattamaggāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.18":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.19":{"pli":"Dvādasa arahattaphalānīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:1.20":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.6:2.1":{"pli":"Na vattabbaṁ—","html":"<p data-doxy='heterodox'>{}"},"kv20.6:2.2":{"pli":"“dvādasavatthukaṁ ñāṇaṁ lokuttaran”ti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.3":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.4":{"pli":"Nanu vuttaṁ bhagavatā—","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.5":{"pli":"“‘idaṁ dukkhaṁ ariyasaccan’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṁ udapādi, ñāṇaṁ udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādi. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.6":{"pli":"‘Taṁ kho panidaṁ dukkhaṁ ariyasaccaṁ pariññeyyan’ti me, bhikkhave …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.7":{"pli":"pariññātanti me, bhikkhave …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.8":{"pli":"‘idaṁ dukkhasamudayaṁ ariyasaccan’ti me, bhikkhave …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.9":{"pli":"‘taṁ kho panidaṁ dukkhasamudayaṁ ariyasaccaṁ pahātabban’ti me, bhikkhave …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.10":{"pli":"pahīnanti me, bhikkhave …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.11":{"pli":"‘idaṁ dukkhanirodhaṁ ariyasaccan’ti me, bhikkhave …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.12":{"pli":"‘taṁ kho panidaṁ dukkhanirodhaṁ ariyasaccaṁ sacchikātabban’ti me, bhikkhave …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.13":{"pli":"sacchikatanti me, bhikkhave …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.14":{"pli":"‘idaṁ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccan’ti me, bhikkhave …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.15":{"pli":"‘taṁ kho panidaṁ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṁ bhāvetabban’ti me, bhikkhave …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.16":{"pli":"bhāvitanti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṁ udapādi …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.17":{"pli":"āloko udapādī”ti. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.18":{"pli":"Attheva suttantoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.19":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv20.6:2.20":{"pli":"Tena hi dvādasavatthukaṁ ñāṇaṁ lokuttaranti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.6:2.21":{"pli":"Ñāṇakathā niṭṭhitā. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}<br>"},"kv20.6:2.22":{"pli":"Vīsatimo vaggo. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv20.6:2.23":{"pli":"Tassuddānaṁ ","html":"<p class='uddana'>{}</p>"},"kv20.6:3.1":{"pli":"Mātughātako ānantariko pitughātako ānantariko arahantaghātako ānantariko ruhiruppādako ānantariko saṅghabhedako ānantariko, natthi puthujjanassa ñāṇaṁ, natthi nirayesu nirayapālā, atthi devesu tiracchānagatā, pañcaṅgiko maggo, dvādasavatthukaṁ ñāṇaṁ lokuttaranti. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"kv20.6:3.2":{"pli":"Catuttho paṇṇāsako. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p>"},"kv20.6:3.3":{"pli":"Tassuddānaṁ ","html":"<p class='uddana'>{}</p>"},"kv20.6:4.1":{"pli":"Niggaho, puññasañcayo, aṭṭhāsi, atītena ca mātughātako. ","html":"<p>{}</p></article>"}},"kv21.1":{"kv21.1:0.1":{"pli":"Kathāvatthu ","html":"<article id='kv21.1'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"kv21.1:0.2":{"pli":"Khuddakaaḍḍhapaṇṇāsaka ","html":"<li>{}</li>"},"kv21.1:0.3":{"pli":"Ekavīsatimavagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"kv21.1:0.4":{"pli":"Sāsanakathā ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"kv21.1:1.1":{"pli":"Sāsanaṁ navaṁ katanti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv21.1:1.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.3":{"pli":"Satipaṭṭhānā navaṁ katāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.4":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.5":{"pli":"sāsanaṁ navaṁ katanti? ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.6":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.7":{"pli":"Sammappadhānā …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.8":{"pli":"iddhipādā …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.9":{"pli":"indriyā …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.10":{"pli":"balā …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.11":{"pli":"bojjhaṅgā navaṁ katāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.12":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.13":{"pli":"pubbe akusalaṁ pacchā kusalaṁ katanti? ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.14":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv21.1:1.15":{"pli":"pubbe sāsavaṁ …pe… saṁyojaniyaṁ ganthaniyaṁ oghaniyaṁ yoganiyaṁ nīvaraṇiyaṁ parāmaṭṭhaṁ upādāniyaṁ …pe… saṅkilesiyaṁ pacchā asaṅkilesiyaṁ katanti? ","html":"{}"},"kv2